‘Tragedies are outpacing life’: In a video address at Davos, Zelensky mourns the dead and pleads for help.

President Volodymyr Zelensky made a passionate appeal by video on Wednesday to heads of state and other decision makers gathered at the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, urging a faster pace of support for his country in the face of Russia’s invasion. Read more

