The top generals from the U.S. and Ukraine meet in Poland, face to face for the first time.

Days before Western allies meet to discuss sending more advanced weaponry, including tanks, to Ukraine, the top U.S. general met with his Ukrainian counterpart in person for the first time on Tuesday in southeastern Poland. Read more

